Description: Karya Desktop Environment
 Modern Turkish desktop environment built on Qt6 and KDE Frameworks 6.
 Features custom window manager, panel system, widget collection,
 and hardware-aware configuration.
 .
 Karya DE is an independent desktop environment (not KDE Plasma)
 designed for Turkish users with NVIDIA/AMD optimization.
 .
 WARNING: First boot will compile the window manager from source.
 This is a one-time process taking 5-15 minutes.
